<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Heilig-Meyers rated buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Heilig-Meyers rated buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers analyst David Childe said he initiated coverage of Heilig-Meyers Co with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- estimated earnings of $0.95 per share for 1997, ending in February, and $1.20 for 1998, versus $0.84 in 1996.</p>
<p>-- shares gained 3/8 to 18-1/4.</p>
</text>
